org.jLOAF.preprocessing.filter.featureSelection

Class FeatureNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jLOAF.preprocessing.filter.featureSelection.FeatureNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FeatureNode>

    public class FeatureNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<FeatureNode>
    Feature Node Class just wraps the weights of features, and holds their statistics information, and provide some methods that are used by filtering algorithms.
    Author:
    Ibrahim Ali Fawaz
